  \u6392\u67E5_\u7ED3\u8BBA_\u6587\u672C: "The process depends on your judgement of whether the issue reproduces. Intermittent issues, config-dependent behavior, load order, or 3+ plugin chains can only be narrowed down, not guaranteed.",
